transcript:
Customer: Yu na mujhko dur kar ab to mujhko khud me sama. Bhakt vatsalay namah, shishi kanthay namah, kripa mujhpe rakhna meri galtiyon ko karte shama. Bhakt vatsalay namah.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Hanji sir, Sandhya bol rahi thi IndiaMART se.
Customer: Achha, free ho gaye mam?
Executive: Hanji sir, aap batao.
Customer: Wo mam, mujhe kam lag gaya, ab mai call karta hu aap se baat.
Executive: To concern me kya karna hai sir?
Customer: Call kar leta hu mai aap se baat.
Executive: Nahi nahi, mai puch rahi hu sir, concern ka kya karna hai sir? Band kar du na aapka concern?
Customer: Han kar do, koi dikkat nahi.
Executive: To aapke paas feedback jayega, aap usse satisfied kar dena. Aur please kal customer care pe call mat kariyega, aap mujhe mere number pe call kariyega.
Customer: Okay okay.
Executive: Han, aur.
summary:
Concerns:

- Customer got busy and wants to call later.

Resolution:

- Executive closed the concern.

- Executive asked to provide feedback.

- Executive asked to call on her number directly.



Next Steps: 

None

Alert (If Any):

None
